.globl triangle
.text
triangle:
beq $a0, 0, invalid
add $t0, $a0, $a1
blt $t0, $a2, invalid
add $t0, $a1, $a2
blt $t0, $a0, invalid
add $t0, $a0, $a2
blt $t0, $a1, invalid
beq $a0, $a1, equilateral
beq $a1, $a2, isosceles
beq $a0, $a2, isosceles
li $v0, 0
j ret
isosceles:
li $v0, 1
j ret
equilateral:
bne $a1, $a2, isosceles
li $v0, 2
j ret
invalid:
li $v0, 3
ret: jr $ra